 "title": "Cabbage-and-cheese shepherd's pie",
 "excerpt": "We all always want to lose a bit of weight. My sister made this version of shepherd's pie last week and I decided to try the healthier option too. You replace the potato top layer with cabbage. It's absolutely delicious. NEEDED: 1 onion and a bit of oil to fry it in …",
 "seo": {
  "title": "Cabbage-and-cheese shepherd's pie - Marinda Kook",
  "description": null
 },
 "html": "<p>We all always want to lose a bit of weight.  My sister made this version of shepherd's pie last week and I decided to try the healthier option too.  You replace the potato top layer with cabbage.  It's absolutely delicious.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-049.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1330\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 049\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-049-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>NEEDED:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 onion and a bit of oil to fry it in</li>\n<li>4 garlic cloves</li>\n<li>2 chillies &#8211; leave out if you don't like spicy food<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1319\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 002\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-002-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>1 kg mince</li>\n<li>1 tin tomato and onion mix<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-013.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1323\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 013\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-013-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>100 ml Worcestershire sauce</li>\n<li>100 ml tomato sauce</li>\n<li>salt and pepper</li>\n<li>15 ml oregano<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1322\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 010\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-010-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>2 cauliflowers<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-015.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1324\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 015\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-015-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>250 ml milk</li>\n<li>100 ml butter &#8211; leave out if you're worried about the fat</li>\n<li>2,5 ml nutmeg</li>\n<li>300 ml grated cheese</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOW:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>slice the onion and fry in a bit of oil until glassy</li>\n<li>finely chop the garlic and chillies and fry together with the onion<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1320\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-003-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>break up the raw mince with a fork and fry until brown together with the onion mixture</li>\n<li>add the tomato sauce, Worcestershire sauce, tomato and onion mix, oregano, salt and pepper<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-023.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1325\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 023\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-023-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>let it simmer for 20 minutes &#8211; if it's too saucy you can thicken the sauce or spoon it off</li>\n<li>spoon the meat into an ovenproof dish &#8211; set aside<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-031.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1327\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 031\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-031-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>finely chop the raw cauliflower in your food processor<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-027.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1326\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 027\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-027-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>put it in a pot on the stove together with the milk, butter and nutmeg &#8211; cook until done</li>\n<li>spoon it on top of the meat mixture<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-034.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1328\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 034\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-034-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>sprinkle cheese over<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-039.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1329\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 039\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-039-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>bake for 20 minutes until the cheese is golden brown at 180 degrees Celsius<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-051.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1331\" alt=\"Herderspastei met blomkool laag blog 051\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Herderspastei-met-blomkool-laag-blog-051-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Together with a salad it's a meal fit for a king.</p>"
}
